c: 3
v: 155
t: "Diggah Nabii Mucammad Åzakáiķe kataysiisow ucud Saaku nammâ Butta (moominiin kee koros kinnuk) edde tongoorowe Ayro Siinik kudeh yan mari, cagalah Sheytan tama dambit ken kah Qidem dambittek tu-abeenimih Sabbata, Nummah Yalli Abeenimik Qafu keenih Abeh, Diggah Yalli dambi cabti- li, xiqleeh isi Amri cine marih digaalat mayasissika"